      <title>法国出生率创婴儿潮结束以来最大降幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/french-childbirths-decline-by-most-since-end-of-baby-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年法国出生人口下降速度加速至半个世纪以来的最快水平，进一步表明法国人口将持续老龄化，增加该国公共财政负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/french-childbirths-decline-by-most-since-end-of-baby-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 16:41:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗的克莱曼表示通货膨胀尚未得到控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-14/apollo-s-kleinman-says-inflation-is-not-tamed-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司联席总裁斯科特·克莱曼警告称，通货膨胀尚未得到控制，利率可能长期维持高位。他接受了彭博社丹尼·伯格的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-14/apollo-s-kleinman-says-inflation-is-not-tamed-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 16:38:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通预计股票回购需求将持续激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/jpmorgan-sees-surge-in-demand-for-equity-backed-repos-persisting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通表示，融资成本上升正蔓延至股票支持的回购协议市场，而且这种现象不太可能减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/jpmorgan-sees-surge-in-demand-for-equity-backed-repos-persisting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 16:35:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>镍危机后 LME 将清算会员资本需求增加三倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/lme-to-triple-clearer-capital-needs-in-post-nickel-crisis-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦金属交易所 (LME) 清算所计划将会员资本要求提高两倍，这是旨在两年多前镍价出现空头挤压危机后强化市场的最新改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/lme-to-triple-clearer-capital-needs-in-post-nickel-crisis-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 16:33:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
