      <title>欧洲股市因阿斯麦和西门子前景看好而反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/european-stocks-edge-higher-before-macro-data-siemens-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西门子股份公司和阿斯麦控股公司的乐观前景帮助市场收复了唐纳德·特朗普大选胜利造成的部分损失，欧洲股市出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/european-stocks-edge-higher-before-macro-data-siemens-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 08:24:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市在反弹后出现“疲态”迹象：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
